{"tid":716654,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［竭澤而漁］「用衛星抓魷魚」大陸壟斷全球6成捕獲量、價格飆漲40%","createTime":"2018-06-25T12:26:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-25T14:58:21.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8147452ff39889bc5db99b667cb8fde2794440a2","tid":716654,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T12:26:15.000Z","msg":"中國大陸致力發展高科技，現在還將技術應用在捕撈海洋生物，據《南華早報》報導，大陸運用衛星資訊來追蹤魷魚，政府還以補貼燃料等方式鼓勵大量捕釣與捕撈，結果創下捕獲量占全球6成的業績，但也造成其他國家捕量大減，南韓的捕撈量在2003年至2017年下降48%，魷魚價格在去年上漲40%，日本的捕撈量則大降73%。<br />\n<br />\n據《南華早報》報導，近年來在國際海域捕撈魷魚的漁船中，有5成至7成來自中國大陸，在全球每年吃掉270萬噸魷魚的情況下，隨著大陸壟斷國際海域6成的捕獲量，市場也受到了影響，大陸將高品質的魷魚留在國內市場使用，並用高價出口低品質的魷魚到國外。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/25/202506_161efd3ff37f85c5b8ac93bc88f2177e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F25%2F202506_161efd3ff37f85c5b8ac93bc88f2177e.png&h=8c49c8ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/25/202528_911f833d92f496d9be07b68ffed312e6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F25%2F202528_911f833d92f496d9be07b68ffed312e6.png&h=4bc135b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲陸媒報導，大陸用衛星抓魷魚，壟斷全球6成捕獲量。（圖／東森新聞資料畫面）<br />\n<br />\n《南華早報》提到，大量捕撈魷魚不僅僅是飲食問題，魷魚捕撈計畫研究員指出，「對於征服全球海洋這趟漫長的路程中，這是非常重要的一小步。」該名研究員表示，北京有成為海洋強權的野心，藉由這樣的活動來增強自己的影響力，對抗其他海洋大國。<br />\n<br />\n《南華早報》指出，大陸漁船每週都會收到政府發送的簡報，當中包含了全球海域最新的魷魚群體的規模和位置，也因為魷魚的生命週期短暫，導致牠們相當難以追縱及預測，研究員難有足夠的時間收集資訊，但大陸政府發布的預報有70%至90%的準確率，主要的原因就是他們使用人造衛星，來打造全球最大魷魚監視網路，提供開放海域中魷魚生長、移動的資訊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://fnc.ebc.net.tw/FncNews/Content/42116\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffnc.ebc.net.tw%2FFncNews%2FContent%2F42116&d=KmpeZqweOkxZceHMK33iMf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=ffa7d124\" target=\"_blank\">https://fnc.ebc.net.tw/FncNews/Content/42116</a>"},{"pid":"e583b784a7eab137c8759f9787d3f4b3d8300aa9","tid":716654,"uid":1655,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T13:48:56.000Z","msg":"屌你啲衛星就係用黎做呢個咁低端既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n支那人真係蝗蟲，除左食乜撚都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a1f3e395d1aedf066dc4edc85510ee73651cc85","tid":716654,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T13:51:19.000Z","msg":"好快就會食到絕種，有得食好食啦"},{"pid":"b6bf1b717adaca27d25da07c0a9f661baa5fe188","tid":716654,"uid":10757,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T13:53:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a3189b4ceee67be553bf30f00da7a45a8d47e00","tid":716654,"uid":59030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T13:57:34.000Z","msg":"黃禍"},{"pid":"8cfe92788f2ffdde6b1afc108fbe69309a462198","tid":716654,"uid":42751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T13:59:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">也因為魷魚的生命週期短暫</span>都唔知係好事定壞事"},{"pid":"345451834c6df966e4fbb1c721cee5e221689a53","tid":716654,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e583b784a7eab137c8759f9787d3f4b3d8300aa9","tid":716654,"uid":1655,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T13:48:56.000Z","msg":"屌你啲衛星就係用黎做呢個咁低端既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n支那人真係蝗蟲，除左食乜撚都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T14:02:04.000Z","msg":"GPS導航系統<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad1bde6a4fb95374fc0b61d630a07f6c8e4d150f","tid":716654,"uid":91813,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T14:22:57.000Z","msg":"連登真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有科技/冇科技都屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\"